{"title": "Oblina", "content": "<div>Brzy započne nová éra světa, v níž budeme trpět!</div><div><br /></div><div><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>A tak umřem chudi</em></span><br /><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>umřeme prosti</em></span><br /><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>se zlatými zuby</em></span><br /><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>v bílé dásni</em></span></div><div><br /></div><div style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>Ty jdeš! Já reptám. -</em></span></div><div style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>Jdi! Nech mne reptat!</em></span></div><div style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>Poctivý muži,</em></span></div><div style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>prchni z této země!</em></span></div><div style=\"text-align:center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align:left\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>Já tebe uctívat? Zač?</em></span></div><div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>Zda jsi kdy nadnášel břímě</em></span></div><div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>tomu, jejž tíží bol?</em></span></div><div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>Zda jsi kdy zkonejšil slzy</em></span></div><div style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em>tomu, hrůzou jenž lká?</em></span></div><div style=\"text-align:left\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align:left\"><br /></div>", "published": "2017-10-20T14:11:00Z", "tags": [], "filename": "/2017/10/oblina.html"}